    L4[Layer 4: ISOLATION<br/>Sub-agents with fresh context · Orchestrator stays lean<br/>Bring back summaries, not transcripts.]
    L5[Layer 5: PROGRESSIVE DISCLOSURE<br/>Load skills/tools/knowledge on demand · Tool masking > removal<br/>Three-layer retrieval.]

